                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For an article by Rear Admiral H. C. Shepheard of the United States Coast Guard
                    and John W. Mann, Acting Adviser on Shipping in the Office of Transport and
                    Communications Policy of the Department of State, concerning the International
                    Conference on Pollution of the Seas and Coasts, held at London April 26–May 12,
                    1954, see the Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, August 30,
                    1954, page 311.</p>
            </div>
